V6.1 - [04/21/2011]
* completely reworked chat windows (may require a /resetui for most users if looks messed up)
* can toggle chat windows outside of combat to be hidden or shown, skada embed support added and auto functions with button at bottom right chat!
* fixed bug where bags datatext panel wasnt class colored when it should of been
* fixed bug where currency datatext panel wasnt class colored when it should of been
* fixed bug where exp/rep bars were disabling but just showing up random places instead of not showing up at all!
* rightbars are now set to vertical by default (can still change to horizontal in config)
* added improved colorpicker frame by Jaslm from ColorPickerPlus
* most of locales finished for ingame config (datatext and some misc need finishing)
* raidicons will no longer be displayed in parties
* tooltip placement adjusted to account for new options
* skada will be hidden when embed active by default to prevent weird issues that require multiple chat button clicks to fix!

